name: Insurance Claim Fraud Detection App for Developers
description: Build ML Model to analyze Healthcare Insurance Claims to detect possible fraud

appStages.name: Introduction
appStages.stageDetails:
{ "components": [ { "label": "HTML", "attrs": [ { "attr": "", "value": "" } ], "content": "

Healthcare Insurance Claims Analytical App

Overview

This application enables detection of potential fraudulent insurance claims using machine learning models. It supports exploratory data analysis, feature engineering, model training, and validationâ€”all aimed at improving the accuracy and efficiency of claim review processes within healthcare insurance operations.

Input

  • + Claim transaction data
  • + User-defined filters to focus on specific claim segments
  • + Model name

Output

  • + Trained classification model for fraud detection in insurance claims
  • + Validation metrics including accuracy, precision, recall, and F1-score
  • + Predicted fraudulent claims based on trained models
  • + Interactive visualizations showing claim distribution and fraud patterns
  • + Insights from analyzing claims across dimensions like organization, city, transaction type, and payment methods

Key Features

  • + Enhances fraud detection using advanced analytics and machine learning
  • + Streamlines claim processing by identifying suspicious patterns early
  • + Improves decision-making through data-driven insights
  • + Reduces financial losses by flagging high-risk claims for investigation
  • + Provides a flexible and configurable interface for model training and validation
", "refreshOnChange": false, "customClass": "

Amount Claimed Amount.
Method Method of Payment.
Duration Treatment duration.
Transfers Amount Transferred.
Outstanding Outstanding Amount.
